	   <tr><td colspan=2>It sounds like Funcom (or whatever) took a page from MicroSoft in releasing software months before it is free from known bugs.  Hopefully, they will provide the free patches and service editions, without using the pay per minute customer support line.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
